# ==========================================================================
# Authorized devices (SOURCE OF TRUTH). The script connects whatever is
# listed here and DISCONNECTS whatever you delete.
#
# Format:   name | serial | ip:port | type
#   - serial : ro.serialno (never changes) -> identifies the device
#   - ip:port : last known WiFi endpoint (ignored in usb mode)
#   - type : usb (permanent cable) | wifi
#
# To ADD a device: ./tablet.sh usb   or   ./tablet.sh qr  (they self-register)
# To REMOVE one:   delete its line.
# ==========================================================================

